 buying Nintendo's console as soon as it is restocked</p><p class="author"><span>By <a href="/articles/?author=1570">James Batchelor</a></span></p><div class="metadata"><span class="timestamp"><i class="fa fa-clock-o"></i> 19 hours ago</span></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="container"><aside class="jobs" id="jobs-2089922"><div class="related-jobs"><p class="section-title">Related Jobs</p><div class="job"><p class="title"><a href="/jobs/view/108293">Technical Director - SUMO SHEFFIELD</a></p><p class="location"><i class="fa fa-map-marker"></i> Anywhere</p><p class="company"><i class="fa fa-building"></i> Sumo Digital</p></div><div class="job"><p class="title"><a href="/jobs/view/111739">Senior Character Artist - SUMO NEWCASTLE</a></p><p class="location"><i class="fa fa-map-marker"></i> Anywhere</p><p class="company"><i class="fa fa-building"></i> Sumo Digital</p></div><div class="job"><p class="title"><a href="/jobs/view/111974">Senior Technical Artist - THE CHINESE ROOM</a></p><p class="location"><i class="fa fa-map-marker"></i> Anywhere</p><p class="company"><i class="fa fa-building"></i> Sumo Digital</p></div><a href="/jobs" class="button">Discover more jobs in games <i class="fa fa-caret-right"></i></a></div></aside></div><div class="container" id="comments"><p class="section-title">Latest comments </p><div class="max-block-width"><p>There are no comments on this article yet. Why not be the first to post one?</p></div></div><div class="container"><p class="section-title">Sign in to contribute</p><div class="composer"><div><form class="form basic" method="post" action=""><fieldset><label>Email address</label><input type="text" name="login_email" id="login_email" title="Email" /><label>Password</label><input type="password" name="login_password" id="login_password" title="Password" /></fieldset><button class="button" type="submit">Sign in</button></form><p>
